Planetary - 1º- SUN
The simbology of the Sun is linked to all the planets, harmonizes like venus, communicates like mercury... etc. it resonates with each planet and expand the qualities of each planet, since the planetary qualities are contained in the Sun. If you want to know more, buy the piece!

"Planetary" is the name of the result of my desire to learn and teach astrology to many people around the world, it is in purpose of growth and desires and magic.
This art is a process of days, therefore they will cost 1 tezo each edition, and the number of pieces is really small since whoever wants to collect the card will also benefit from extended information that I will send about the qualities of that planet.


If you bought a piece and I didn't see it and you want your extended information about the sun, write to me at caro.lettieri96@gmail.com with subject: NFT SUN
